{"build_type":"library","description":"Launcher wrapper whose whole body is one tail-chain launch of the single-artifact worker. The artifact loop calls this once per artifact (after setting g_rec_cur_artifact_idx): the tail launch spawns the worker in its own arena, awaits its single result, and returns it, so the loop continues serially after each worker's arena is reclaimed.","module_name":"run-one-artifact-worker-launcher","package_name":"run-one-artifact-worker-launcher","function_definitions":{"run-one-artifact-worker-launcher":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"request","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"launch_worker_binary","target_binary":"build-one-artifact-by-current-index-as-worker","cycle_type":"tail-chain","input":"request"}]}}}